languages.en: //(0,4.37)\\Well, it certainly appears that Yuki Yamazaki is a fan of yoga.//(4.37,8.75)\\A schedule near the hot springs reveals that she has booked the trainer all day.//(8.75,38.75)\\Feeling flexible, 47?

languages.es: //(0,4.300982)\\Bueno, parece que a Yuki Yamazaki le gusta el yoga.//(4.300982,9.113)\\El horario que figura cerca de las fuentes termales indica que ha reservado a un instructor para todo el día.//(9.113,39.113)\\¿Cómo va esa flexibilidad, 47?
